sentences: Heidi Musum (born 22 June 1993), better known by her stage name Kamferdrops, is a Norwegian singer and songwriter.

She first achieved recognition in Sweden and Norway in 2017, after her cover of Ole Ivars and Kikki Danielsson's 1999 song "Jag trodde Ã¤nglarna fanns" became a number-two hit in Sweden and top forty hit in Norway.
Kamferdrops competed in Melodifestivalen 2018 with the song "Solen lever kvar hos dig".
